params.name: embedding_size
params.description: Dimensionality (hidden size) for the embedding layer.

params.name: depths
params.description: Depth (number of layers) for each stage.

params.name: layer_type
params.description: The layer to use, it can be either x or y. An xlayer is a ResNets BottleNeck layer withreductionfixed to1. While a ylayer is ax` but with squeeze and excitation. Please refer to thepaper for a detailed explanation of how these layers were constructed.

params.name: hidden_act
params.description: The non-linear activation function in each block. If string, gelu, relu, selu and gelu_neware supported.

params.name: downsample_in_first_stage
params.description: If True, the first stage will downsample the inputs using a stride of 2.
